title: Dog and Beth On The Hunt S02E03 Love Conquers All WS DSR x264-NY
description:
In an inspiring story of family and faith, Dog and Beth visit their friends Royce and Alesia Kyser in Foley, Ala. Royce was recently diagnosed with lung cancer, and Alesia desperately needs help catching their jumps and keeping the business on track. Can Dog and Beth train Royce's children to take over the business and carry on the family legacy?
